query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(it1 mii) NoMergeJoin(it1 mii t) NoMergeJoin(it1 mii t ci) NoNestLoop(ci it1 mii t n) NoNestLoop(ci it1 mii n pi t it2) */ select min(n.name),
min(t.title)
from info_type AS it1
inner join movie_info_idx AS mii
on it1.id = mii.info_type_id AND it1.info ilike 'rating' AND ( mii.info ilike '0%' OR mii.info ilike '1%' OR mii.info ilike '2%')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mii.movie_id
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on ci.person_id = n.id
inner join person_info AS pi
on n.id = pi.person_id AND pi.info ilike '%USA%'
inner join info_type AS it2
on pi.info_type_id = it2.id AND it2.info ilike '%birth%';
